node.text: AD I Our journey to getting pregnant was a very long and emotional one. You guys have been asking... and yes. We would love a second baby anytime and we have talked through what that would look like. Our friends @enfamil have made our first feeding journey so much easier than we could have imagined and we can't thank them enough for their partnership. If you’re a new or expecting parent, head to the link in my bio to shop Enfamil formulas – it’s the only leading brand with an expert-recommended amount of DHA. #Enfamil #FueltheWonder
